						<summary>

						<p>On a stone slab erected in the field of an individual.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Kaṉṉaradēva Year 23: 962 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records that uḍaiyāṉ Mūrtti Tāyaṉ of Vāyalūrppāḍi in Ugaḷūr-kūṟṟam made a gift of 1/8 <hi rend="italic">vēli</hi> of land after purchase from the <hi rend="italic">ūrār</hi> of Porōsappāḍi Iḍaichchiṟu Vāyilūr and endowed it as <hi rend="italic">ēripaṭṭi</hi> (for the maintenance of tank). </p>						

						</summary>
